data.description: Price Reduced to Sell Fast. Warm, Cozy & Spacious w/ All the right touches. 4 Bdrms, Den, Loft, 3.5 Baths, 3CG, Heated Pool w/ Spa & 2 New AC Units 2023!!  Pool area is Serene w/ built in Gas BBQ, artificial turf & custom fire pit. Great for entertaining, pool fun or quiet evening BBQ's w/ lots of backyard Privacy. Home is spacious w/ Plantation Shutters throughout! Kitchen sports SS Appliances, Granite Countertops, Refinished Cabinets, Pantry, 1 Gas Range/Oven, 1 Wall Oven & 1 Microwave Convection Oven!  Custom Stair Rail into the Large Loft!  Master Bdrm is huge w/ sitting area & spacious Master Bath.  3 Bdrms share 2 Full baths.  Decorative Stone Gas Fireplace in Family Room.  Lots of exterior Pavers in Front & Back.  RV Gate!   Great Up & Coming location near 202 & 60 hwy access.
